events.name: New York Knicks at Detroit Pistons

headlines.description: — Jalen Brunson scored 15 of his 36 points in the first quarter as the New York Knicks beat Detroit 128-98 on Friday for their 16th straight victory over the Pistons.
headlines.shortLinkText: Brunson scores 36, Knicks rout Pistons 128-98 for 16th straight win over Detroit

headlines.description: — Cam Thomas scored 10 of his 32 points in the fourth quarter to help the Brooklyn Nets beat the Chicago Bulls 120-112 on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Can Thomas scores 32 points in the Nets' 120-112 victory over the Bulls

events.name: Los Angeles Lakers at Toronto Raptors

headlines.description: — Anthony Davis scored a season-high 38 points and had 12 rebounds, LeBron James had 27 points and 10 assists, and the Los Angeles Lakers never trailed in a 131-125 win over the Toronto Raptors on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Davis scores season-high 38, Lakers beat Raptors 131-125 for first road win of the season

events.name: Indiana Pacers at New Orleans Pelicans

headlines.description: — Zion Williamson had 34 points and 10 assists, Brandon Ingram added 26 points and the New Orleans Pelicans snapped a three-game skid with a 125-118 victory over the Indiana Pacers on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Zion Williamson has 34 points and 10 assists to lead Pelicans past Pacers, 125-118

events.name: Oklahoma City Thunder at Portland Trail Blazers
